{
  "stem": "17761.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 139.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And another was the name of D-A-N, who was the terror of the ghetto, because he had a very strong hand, and he used to hit people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were weak.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you couldn't hit back or something like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These two guys they used also to come to these presentations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They also published some bulletin, in which they told about their lives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't have anything of these.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there is one of those children, that I know of, when she came out, she wrote a little letter to Ilya Ehrenburg in Russia, who collected letters from children after the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there, she appears with her little letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There-- it wasn't a wall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were limits.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you went out of the ghetto, you were sentenced to death.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only in the market.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Mogilev, there was a market.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, they used to bring all kind of products.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that is one thing that I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they had the German, whose domain, and they were all non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it wasn't a relationship that I became close friends with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's the reason that, in addition to the fact that I never went to public school, I didn't go to any high school, either.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the only school I had there, that school of life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I learned a lot of things there, which are important.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even I learned how to cope with very difficult situations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sisters, no-- they were little children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father worked occasionally.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to sing occasionally, and people used to come, because it was a very beautiful voice, and just used to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
